  planner_response {
    thinking: "**Verifying Code Success**\n\nI\'ve just successfully compiled the code with a perfect green result! Before I prepare a summary, I\'m doing a final check to ensure everything is in order.\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "### DeFi Anti-Rekt (Kamino + Derive) Project Landing Page\n\nI have built a highly styled, dark-themed, and responsive landing page for the **DeFi Anti-Rekt Infrastructure Protocol**. The application is structured with rigorous adherence to your structural requirements, displaying a cinematic and moody aesthetic utilizing a warm cream color palette with elegant micro-interactions.\n\n---\n\n### Core Structural Features & Achievements\n\n- **Visual Identity (`index.html` & `src/index.css`)**:\n  - **Typography Pairing**: Loaded the global display font **Almarai** and paired it with **Instrument Serif** (italic only) inside the head element to serve as the editorial italic text accent.\n  - **Warm Cream Color System**: Integrated style rules matching the `#E1E0CC` palette and defined the Tailwind CSS `@theme` containing the primary color (`#DEDBC8`) and serif font-family block.\n  - **Fractal Noise Overlays**: Implemented two custom SVG inline filter classes (`.noise-overlay` and `.bg-noise`) to produce a fine-grained, high-end organic analog texture.\n\n- **Section 1: The Cinematic Hero (`src/components/Hero.tsx`)**:\n  - **Inset Framework**: Positioned a padded outer container creating a screen offset border, with a full-viewport looping cinematic MP4 background.\n  - **Hanging Navbar Pill**: Positioned a dark navigation list at the absolute top center with responsive compression metrics and inline transparency levels.\n  - **Staggered Header Pull-Up**: Applied a `WordsPullUp` animation that splits text by spaces and slides words sequentially from `y:20` to `y:0`. Includes an absolute superscript asterisk (`*`) positioned precisely relative to the ending character.\n  - **Animated Sub-Text & CTA**: Programmed a custom bottom grid matching your exact ease boundaries `[0.16, 1, 0.3, 1]` with an interactive \"Protect Loan\" pill that controls an expandable icon container.\n\n- **Section 2: The Core Concept (`src/components/Concept.tsx`)**:\n  - Contains the multi-style `WordsPullUpMultiStyle` heading that dynamically segregates font styles to isolate italic serif structures.\n  - **Scroll-Linked Character Reveal**: Built an `AnimatedCharacterParagraph` which maps a viewport `useScroll` motion values index over total characters, dynamically staggering individual letter opacities from `0.2` to `1` within the scroll margins.\n\n- **Section 3: Protocol Architecture (`src/components/Architecture.tsx`)**:\n  - Structured card elements into a 4-column balanced bento-grid, converting dynamically from single column on mobile structures to multi-column on desktop. It triggers staggered entrance scale transitions upon viewport entrance.\n  - Includes a background-looping video card, and modular details presenting Kamino supply APR, Derive hedging option puts, and deep routing check actions.\n\n- **Interactive Core dApp Simulator (`src/components/InteractiveWidget.tsx`)**:\n  - Connected the main CTA triggers to a full math simulator modal. Users can slide Solomon (SOL) collateral variables and index prices to immediately monitor how Kamino yield dynamically covers, subsidizes, and pays for the underlying Derive put option premium.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      nanos: 679047258
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
